October is Cybersecurity Awareness Month! Strengthen your account security.

Across all your online accounts, signing in is the front door to your  
personal information. One thing you can do this month is to ensure this  
front door is well protected. Check out three tips from Google to help you  
stay safer online.

Create and save secure passwords

Keep your accounts safer with unique passwords, without having to remember  
them! Built into Chrome and Android, Google Password Manager creates,  
securely saves, and fills in passwords for all of your online accounts. It  
also lets you know if any of your saved passwords have been found in a  
breach.

