Help make the Internet safer for everyone with 2-Step Verification

One thing we can all do to help prevent widespread cyber attacks is to  
strengthen our own account security. 2-Step Verification adds a second step  
to verify that it’s you, so even if a hacker steals your password, they  
can’t get into your account.

